<p><span>Ingrédients : </span>Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Sodium Benzoate, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Parfum (Fragrance), Sodium Lauroyl Sarcosinate, Propylene Glycol, Panthenol, Citric Acid, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Flower Extract, Sodium Hydroxide, Potassium Sorbate. </p>
